The cli shall accept aears file input
When validation requested the cli shall check syntax
When generation requested the cli shall output UML
The cli shall generate PlantUML format by default
When report format requested the cli shall output text analysis
When title flag provided the cli shall include diagram title
When stats flag provided the cli shall include requirement statistics
When no-relationships flag provided the cli shall exclude actor relationships
When output file specified the cli shall save generated content to file
The cli shall extract actors from entities in UML output
The cli shall extract use cases from functionalities in UML output
The cli shall create relationships between actors and use cases
IF generation fails THEN the cli shall exit with error code
IF file invalid THEN the cli shall exit with error code